定的支出计划。 打个比方，这个债务上限，就像是美国财政部的“信用卡额度”，批准这个“额度”，要通过美国国会。从1917年美国设置债务上限至今，美国债务上限已经提高了超过100次，额度也从最初的450亿美元，大幅提升至2021年的31.4万亿美元。美国众议院通过债务上限法案 1917年至今提高上限超100次"},"attached_info":"Cj4I6cjD38Xa+LcjEAMaCDk2NTg5ODQzIMu15aMGMAE4J0AHcgk2MDQzOTMxOTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"86 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1685729727.8623126","card_id":"Q_604406455","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":604406455,"title":"如何看待谢娜获得《乘风 2023》二公第一名？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/604406455","type":"question","created":1685682804,"answer_count":38,"follower_count":39,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[10438,11334,22839,123556,2630221],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"谢娜在《乘风 2023》第二次公演中表演了《面纱》"},"attached_info":"Cj4I6cjD38Xa+LcjEAMaCDk2NTkyNzQzIPT05aMGMAA4J0AIcgk2MDQ0MDY0NTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"83 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1685729727.8627992","card_id":"Q_603596848","target":{"id":603596848,"title":"做网页开发时，允许用户输入url图片地址来作为自己的头像有什么风险？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/603596848","type":"question","created":1685327203,"answer_count":24,"follower_count":60,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[213,225,708,1567],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I6cjD38Xa+LcjEAMaCDk2NDEzMDc5IOOa0KMGMAA4PEAJcgk2MDM1OTY4NDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"73 万热度","trend